main.name: Amber Steele
main.description: Hi, I'm Amber Steele with Atlantic Real Estate Broker.  Choosing to sell your home or to purchase a new one can often be an overwhelming experience. That is why choosing the right realtor is so important. As your realtor, I can minimize the stress and help make the process go smoothly.   Don’t like having meetings in an office? No worries, let’s go to the park, coffee shop, even a bar.
main.bio: Whether you are looking for a spacious empty nester home in the foothills of the blue ridge, to a starter home in the suburbs, to a studio apartment closer to the city, I am here to help. I am easily accessible and will typically respond within the business day. If you are looking to buy or sell your home in the atlanta area, know that I am committed to you, and your satisfaction. Be sure to give me a call for all of you real estate needs.
